name: Children's Chevron Gift Tags
description:
12 Gift tags / Enclosure Cards. 

*These little tags are a simple and charming way to personalize your gift-giving. Slip one into a bag, tape one to a box, or tie one around a bottle of wine for a house-warming gift! The back of each card is left blank for you to write a personal message for the recipient, if you desire. 

*Cards measure 3" x 3.5" and are printed on smooth, heavy weight card stock.

*Children's Cards include the message, "a gift for you from your friend" unless otherwise specified. Adult cards do not include a message unless otherwise specified.

*Don't forget to specify the name or names you would like printed on your cards! In the "Other Comments" section, type exactly how you want your cards to read. (Example: "Jane Doe" / "Carrie" / "the Smiths" / "Jack and Lisa")
